title: Picnic Time's Cart Cooler 545
transcripts: The cart cooler by picnic time is the perfect all around cooler tote on wheels the tote is fully removable from the trolley and has two large storage pockets on each side and a large zipper opening for easy accessibility the cart cooler is lined with an insulated foil interior and has a removable heat-sealed water-resistant liner that holds up to 37 cans it's made of polyester microfiber and sits on a sturdy lightweight folding trolley complete with large extra wide wheels and stability bar to keep it upright when it's not rolling it also has a split-level comfort grip handle that provides to handle heights for added comfort the car cooler provides you with a convenient nearly effortless way to track your hot or cold items or groceries around in style the car cooler is perfect for trips to the beach family gatherings the park or shopping at the farmers market.
